  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Loading a Saved Plan\n",
    "\n",
    "A saved plan can be loaded by calling `ae.plan.load_json(plan_path)` (for local plans) or `ae.plan.load(plan_id)` (for remote plans)."
   ]
